{"tid":2302722,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"全港各界譴責老舞群組涉嫌干犯國安法恐怖活動罪","createTime":"2020-11-27T10:29:20.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-27T11:56:49.000Z","uid":335967,"like":19,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"d466e3e2acc55a051148dcf3db23caf05e618f18","tid":2302722,"uid":335967,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-27T10:29:20.000Z","msg":"聲明<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n自本月初，逾百人於多個地點進行政治性聚集(即老舞大會)。 其中大部分人無視防疫指引， 在未有佩戴口罩的情況下進行近距離接觸，事後多名出席者證實感染中國武漢冠狀病毒。 全港各界就有關政治活動無視疫情風險，危害公共衛生及破壞社會安寧，予以譴責。另外，有關政治性集結已涉嫌違反《港區國安法》第二十四條中「威嚇公眾以圖實現政治主張，組織、策劃、實施、參與實施以傳染病病原體造成嚴重社會危害的恐怖活動」。 對於特區政府及香港警方 未有作出任何拘捕，蓄意縱容恐怖活動，危害國家安全，作出最嚴厲譴責。"},{"pid":"eea6d8af267cd6002bdb48478bda370a7187e5fe","tid":2302722,"uid":335967,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-27T10:29:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"870a2425157108ad10c76abfaaa8c3f1e5dd9f27","tid":2302722,"uid":304873,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-27T10:30:01.000Z","msg":"推！"},{"pid":"61ce55784ab983c4607583eca8025d6c1d125730","tid":2302722,"uid":54728,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-11-27T10:30:54.000Z","msg":"林作第一個應該指佢老母出嚟"},{"pid":"c959a1b4c09fc5fb5d44884780db16fd5946de23","tid":2302722,"uid":335967,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-27T10:31:14.000Z","msg":"副本抄送: 香港國安處，支联辦，各大傳媒"},{"pid":"976de4cbfda44302886303d72aa87ee085713a8f","tid":2302722,"uid":335967,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"61ce55784ab983c4607583eca8025d6c1d125730","tid":2302722,"uid":54728,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-11-27T10:30:54.000Z","msg":"林作第一個應該指佢老母出嚟"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-27T10:31:37.000Z","msg":"不孝子<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal